title: Sam Mostyn - Wikipedia
snippet: Samantha Joy Mostyn (/ˈmɒstən/ MOSS-tən; born 13 September 1965) is an Australian businesswoman and advocate, who has served as the 28th governor-general of Australia since 1 July 2024.
